description:
This package provides backward-compatible versions of Windows UI features including UWP XAML controls, dense control styles, and Fluent styles and materials. It is part of the Windows UI Library.

Please note that the APIs contained in this package are subject to change before the official WinUI 3.0 release. This version is intended for preview and not for use in shipping applications.
title: Microsoft Windows UI Library
